<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2852] RAMInputStream hits false EOF if you seek to EOF then seek back then readBytes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2852</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;TestLazyLoadThreadSafety fails in hudson, possibly an issue with RAMDirectory.&lt;br/&gt;
If you hack lucene testcase to return another directory, the same seed will pass.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12494963">LUCENE-2852</key>
            <summary>RAMInputStream hits false EOF if you seek to EOF then seek back then readBytes</summary>
